<!DOCTYPE html><html><head prefix="og: http://ogp.me/ns# fb: http://ogp.me/ns/fb# medium-com: http://ogp.me/ns/fb/medium-com#"><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1" user-scalable="no"><title>Love what you build. Build what you love. — Medium</title><link rel="canonical" href="https://medium.com/@apitt24/love-what-you-build-build-what-you-love-9cedbb05e32f"><meta name="title" content="Love what you build. Build what you love."><meta name="referrer" content="always"><meta name="description" content="10 things Product Managers must do"><meta property="og:site_name" content="Medium"><meta property="og:title" content="Love what you build. Build what you love."><meta property="og:url" content="https://medium.com/@apitt24/love-what-you-build-build-what-you-love-9cedbb05e32f"><meta property="og:image" content="https://d262ilb51hltx0.cloudfront.net/max/800/1*A0_hN1TDishFoOC7ZNVetg.png"><meta property="fb:app_id" content="542599432471018"><meta property="og:description" content="10 things Product Managers must do"><meta name="twitter:site" content="@Medium"><meta name="twitter:image:src" content="https://d262ilb51hltx0.cloudfront.net/max/800/1*A0_hN1TDishFoOC7ZNVetg.png"><link rel="publisher" href="https://plus.google.com/103654360130207659246"><link rel="author" href="https://medium.com/@apitt24"><meta name="author" content="Adam Pittenger"><meta property="og:type" content="article"><meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image"><meta property="article:publisher" content="https://www.facebook.com/medium"><meta property="article:author" content="https://medium.com/@apitt24"><meta property="article:published_time" content="2013-11-15T15:44:47.403Z"><meta name="twitter:creator" content="@apitt24"><meta name="apple-itunes-app" content="app-id=828256236, app-argument=medium:/p/9cedbb05e32f"><meta name="twitter:app:name:iphone" content="Medium"><meta name="twi